Package UI

Class LowerCard

java.lang.Object
UI.LowerCard
public class LowerCard extends Object
Represents the lower card panel in the UI, handling the configuration of chart types such as Pie, Line, and Bar charts. This class provides a user interface for selecting chart types, data sources, and other settings related to charts.
